'''1913年大西洋飓风季'''是连续第三个在六月前就至少发展出一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]的大西洋飓风季，不过当时“大西洋飓风季”尚未正式定义，现今则是以每年6月1日正式开始，同年11月30日结束<ref name="FAQG1">{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-11-28 | deadurl = no | author = Neal Dorst | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 1993 | accessdate = 2016-12-09 | title = When is hurricane season ? | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161128092855/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html }}</ref>。全季第一个热带低气压于5月5日形成，最后一个天气系统于10月30日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。8月30日至9月4日，本季第七和第八个热带气旋同时存在。

全季十个热带气旋中有六个成为热带风暴，四个增强成飓风，但都没有达到[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]标准，即都没有达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的三级飓风强度{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，是[[1900年大西洋飓风季|1900年]]后第六个没有大型飓风的大西洋飓风季<ref name="ACE" />。本季最强飓风的[[最大持续风速|最高风速]]为每小时140公里，只达一级飓风标准，但在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]导致五人死亡，损失数额至少有400万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失数额均为1913年[[美元|美元]]价值。|group="注"}}。全季首场飓风也在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]夺走一条人命，第五号飓风则在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]造成价值至少75000美元的破坏。

这年飓风季的低迷活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值仅36<ref>{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040342/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带天气系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告，并且[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的指数不会计入累积数值。<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref><ref name="ACE">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | title = Atlantic Basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | date = 2014-02 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-09 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-04-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425073956/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>

